check.action:
Multi-worktree. Invoke worktree-setup N times, ONCE PER PLAN:
for each plan_n in 1..{{plan_count}}:
  - ticket_slug = {{ticket_slug}}
  - primary_tag = {{primary_tag}}
  - plan_count = {{plan_count}}
  - parallel_safe = true
  - plan_index = plan_n

  Capture {{plan_n.branch}}, {{plan_n.worktree_path}}.

substep.action:
For each plan doc, edit frontmatter (or body) to record:
- branch: {{branch_for_this_plan}}
- worktree_path: {{path_for_this_plan}}

This persists the worktree association across sessions; a
resumption knows where to dispatch workers.
